{"word":"Gifts from God","slug":"gifts-from-god","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gifts from God</b> Spiritual:<br/> - Christ, the Savior<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=6'>Isa 42:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=55&verse=4'>Isa 55:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=16'>Joh 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=10'>Joh 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=33'>Joh 6:33</a> <br/> - The Holy Spirit, the Comforter<br/> <a href='S:Holy Spirit'>Holy Spirit</a> <br/> - Grace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=4&verse=6'>Jas 4:6</a> <br/> - Wisdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=2&verse=6'>Pro 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=5'>Jas 1:5</a> <br/> - Repentance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=18'>Act 11:18</a> <br/> - Faith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=2&verse=8'>Eph 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=29'>Phi 1:29</a> <br/> Temporal:<br/> - Food and raiment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=25'>Mat 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=33'>Mat 6:33</a> <br/> - Rain and fruitful seasons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=22'>Gen 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27&verse=28'>Gen 27:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=5'>Lev 26:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=23'>Isa 30:23</a> <br/> - Wisdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Ch 1:12</a> <br/> - Peace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=6'>Lev 26:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=22&verse=9'>1Ch 22:9</a> <br/> To be used and enjoyed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=3&verse=13'>Ecc 3:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=5&verse=20'>Ecc 5:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=4&verse=5'>1Ti 4:5</a><br/> Should cause us to remember God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=18'>Deu 8:18</a><br/> All creatures partake of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=136&verse=25'>Psa 136:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=145&verse=16'>Psa 145:16</a><br/> Prayer for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=10&verse=1'>Zec 10:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=11'>Mat 6:11</a><br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to both temporal and spiritual<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=4&verse=7'>Psa 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=21&verse=2'>Psa 21:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=34&verse=10'>Psa 34:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=18'>Psa 68:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=35'>Psa 68:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=29&verse=11'>Psa 29:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=11'>Psa 84:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=26'>Ecc 2:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=42&verse=5'>Isa 42:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=11&verse=19'>Eze 11:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=23'>Dan 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=11